{"tid":633703,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"拖延症候群之執行力低到","createTime":"2018-04-18T14:15:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-19T17:36:05.000Z","uid":38732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3171493c1862401e0eab1d5357a4158e208c52a4","tid":633703,"uid":38732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:15:39.000Z","msg":"見到隔離巴打個po講後悔冇勤力讀書。比起依樣，我反而諗到到依家自己出到社會做嘢，都係做一樣嘢，拖十世。其實明明個腦有好多諗法，但唔知點解硬係唔想做佢出嚟，有時會諗可能係太多濕星嘢煩，所以集中唔到。<br />\n<br />\n但諗返轉頭，係自己成日拖拖拖，一拖得耐，仲覺得壓力山大，係咁瞓壓力教，然後又開始做唔到嘢嘅輪迴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實以前實書嗰時都deadline fight，不過總會有力fight，唔知點解出到嚟做嘢先成日力不從心咁。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">執行力 0</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都係咁？一齊集集氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e590094ff0d4c86b6656f95b934feeed274c4a01","tid":633703,"uid":15080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"Same here 一事無成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cf9921007a9bd9b20b43eafa185049f45829a0","tid":633703,"uid":42762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:19:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係"},{"pid":"96307ec3896b9d0c991db153eb2d79fbed2ca9b4","tid":633703,"uid":38732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e590094ff0d4c86b6656f95b934feeed274c4a01","tid":633703,"uid":15080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:16:51.000Z","msg":"Same here 一事無成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"其實我份工係自己想做嘅嘢 <br />\n但都係咁<br />\n我諗緊係咪deadline fight開 搞到個人咁"},{"pid":"e6a9feec53ce2941a033b8ba96d11c55195717ec","tid":633703,"uid":38732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e590094ff0d4c86b6